---
By: Sivananda
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 116
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Ego/Vanity
---
To the one devoid of ego, the whole world is a heaven of rest, a realm of
peace and a kingdom abounding in all happiness. He who has no ego and who
has surrendered himself to God is the master of every power and force.
